{"tha-ap390:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap390:0.2":"Avataphalavagga ","tha-ap390:0.3":"Panasaphaladayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap390:1.1":"“Ajjuno nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap390:1.2":"himavante vasi tada; ","tha-ap390:1.3":"Caranena ca sampanno, ","tha-ap390:1.4":"samadhikusalo muni. ","tha-ap390:2.1":"Kumbhamattam gahetvana, ","tha-ap390:2.2":"panasam jivajivakam; ","tha-ap390:2.3":"Chattapanne thapetvana, ","tha-ap390:2.4":"adasim satthuno aham. ","tha-ap390:3.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap390:3.2":"yam phalamadadim tada; ","tha-ap390:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap390:3.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap390:4.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap390:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap390:4.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap390:5.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap390:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap390:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap390:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap390:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap390:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap390:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma panasaphaladayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap390:8.1":"Panasaphaladayakattherassapadanam atthamam. "}